{"id":39,"parent_id":4,"book_id":4,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":39,"title":"D&C 35","subtitle":"","short_title":"D&C","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Section 35"],[".studyIntro",["i","Revelation given to Joseph Smith the Prophet and Sidney Rigdon, at or near Fayette, New York, December 7, 1830. At this time, the Prophet was engaged almost daily in making a translation of the Bible. The translation was begun as early as June 1830, and both Oliver Cowdery and John Whitmer had served as scribes. Since they had now been called to other duties, Sidney Rigdon was called by divine appointment to serve as the Prophet’s scribe in this work (see",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.20"},"verse 20"],"). As a preface to the record of this revelation, Joseph Smith’s history states: “In December Sidney Rigdon came [from Ohio] to inquire of the Lord, and with him came Edward Partridge. … Shortly after the arrival of these two brethren, thus spake the Lord.”"]],[".studySummary",["i",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.1-2"},"1–2"],", How men may become the sons of God;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.3-7"},"3–7"],", Sidney Rigdon is called to baptize and to confer the Holy Ghost;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.8-12"},"8–12"],", Signs and miracles are wrought by faith;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.13-16"},"13–16"],", The Lord’s servants will thresh the nations by the power of the Spirit;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.17-19"},"17–19"],", Joseph Smith holds the keys of the mysteries;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.20-21"},"20–21"],", The elect will abide the day of the Lord’s coming;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.22-27"},"22–27"],", Israel will be saved."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.1","order":"06.05.035.4092"},["b","1"],"Listen to the voice of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"Lord"],"your God, even",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"Alpha and Omega"],", the beginning and the end, whose",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"course"],"is one",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_1d"},"eternal"],"round, the",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_1e"},"same"],"today as yesterday, and forever."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.2","order":"06.05.035.4093"},["b","2"],"I am Jesus Christ, the Son of God, who was",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"crucified"],"for the sins of the world, even as many as will",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"believe"],"on my name, that they may become the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_2c"},"sons"],"of God, even",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_2d"},"one"],"in",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_2e"},"me"],"as I am",["sup","f"],["a",{"href":"fn_2f"},"one"],"in the Father, as the Father is one in me, that we may be one."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.3","order":"06.05.035.4094"},["b","3"],"Behold, verily, verily, I say unto my servant Sidney, I have looked upon thee and thy works. I have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"heard"],"thy prayers, and prepared thee for a greater work."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.4","order":"06.05.035.4095"},["b","4"],"Thou art blessed, for thou shalt do great things. Behold thou wast sent forth, even as",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"John"],", to prepare the way before me, and before",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"Elijah"],"which should come, and thou knewest it not."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.5","order":"06.05.035.4096"},["b","5"],"Thou didst baptize by water unto repentance, but they",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"received not"],"the Holy Ghost;"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.6","order":"06.05.035.4097"},["b","6"],"But now I give unto thee a commandment, that thou shalt",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"baptize"],"by water, and they shall receive the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"Holy Ghost"],"by the laying on of the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_6c"},"hands"],", even as the apostles of old."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.7","order":"06.05.035.4098"},["b","7"],"And it shall come to pass that there shall be a great work in the land, even among the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"Gentiles"],", for their",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"folly"],"and their abominations shall be made manifest in the eyes of all people."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.8","order":"06.05.035.4099"},["b","8"],"For I am God, and mine arm is not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"shortened"],"; and I will show",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"miracles"],",",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_8c"},"signs"],", and wonders, unto all those who",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_8d"},"believe"],"on my name."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.9","order":"06.05.035.4100"},["b","9"],"And whoso shall ask it in my name in",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"faith"],", they shall",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"cast out"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_9c"},"devils"],"; they shall heal the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_9d"},"sick"],"; they shall cause the blind to receive their",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_9e"},"sight"],", and the deaf to hear, and the dumb to speak, and the lame to walk."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.10","order":"06.05.035.4101"},["b","10"],"And the time",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"speedily"],"cometh that great things are to be shown forth unto the children of men;"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.11","order":"06.05.035.4102"},["b","11"],"But",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"without faith"],"shall not anything be shown forth except",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"desolations"],"upon",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_11c"},"Babylon"],", the same which has made",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_11d"},"all"],"nations drink of the wine of the wrath of her",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_11e"},"fornication"],"."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.12","order":"06.05.035.4103"},["b","12"],"And there are",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"none"],"that doeth good except those who are ready to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"receive"],"the fulness of my gospel, which I have sent forth unto this generation."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.13","order":"06.05.035.4104"},["b","13"],"Wherefore, I call upon the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"weak"],"things of the world, those who are",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"unlearned"],"and despised, to thresh the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_13c"},"nations"],"by the power of my",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_13d"},"Spirit"],";"],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.14","order":"06.05.035.4105"},["b","14"],"And their arm shall be my arm, and I will be their",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"shield"],"and their buckler; and I will gird up their loins, and they shall fight manfully for me; and their",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"enemies"],"shall be under their feet; and I will let",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_14c"},"fall"],"the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_14d"},"sword"],"in their behalf, and by the",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_14e"},"fire"],"of mine indignation will I preserve them."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.15","order":"06.05.035.4106"},["b","15"],"And the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"poor"],"and the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"meek"],"shall have the gospel preached unto them, and they shall be",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_15c"},"looking"],"forth for the time of my coming, for it is",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_15d"},"nigh"],"at hand—"],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.16","order":"06.05.035.4107"},["b","16"],"And they shall learn the parable of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"fig tree"],", for even now already summer is nigh."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.17","order":"06.05.035.4108"},["b","17"],"And I have sent forth the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"fulness"],"of my gospel by the hand of my servant Joseph; and in weakness have I blessed him;"],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.18","order":"06.05.035.4109"},["b","18"],"And I have given unto him the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"keys"],"of the mystery of those things which have been",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"sealed"],", even things which were from the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_18c"},"foundation"],"of the world, and the things which shall come from this time until the time of my coming, if he",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_18d"},"abide"],"in me, and if not,",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_18e"},"another"],"will I plant in his stead."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.19","order":"06.05.035.4110"},["b","19"],"Wherefore, watch over him that his faith fail not, and it shall be given by the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"Comforter"],", the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"Holy Ghost"],", that knoweth all things."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.20","order":"06.05.035.4111"},["b","20"],"And a commandment I give unto thee—that thou shalt",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"write"],"for him; and the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_20b"},"scriptures"],"shall be given, even as they are in mine own bosom, to the salvation of mine own",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_20c"},"elect"],";"],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.21","order":"06.05.035.4112"},["b","21"],"For they will hear my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"voice"],", and shall",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_21b"},"see"],"me, and shall not be",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_21c"},"asleep"],", and shall",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_21d"},"abide"],"the day of my",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_21e"},"coming"],"; for they shall be",["sup","f"],["a",{"href":"fn_21f"},"purified"],", even as I am pure."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.22","order":"06.05.035.4113"},["b","22"],"And now I say unto you,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"tarry"],"with him, and he shall journey with you; forsake him not, and surely these things shall be fulfilled."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.23","order":"06.05.035.4114"},["b","23"],"And",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"inasmuch"],"as ye do not write, behold, it shall be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_23b"},"given"],"unto him to prophesy; and thou shalt preach my gospel and call on",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_23c"},"the holy prophets"],"to prove his words, as they shall be given him."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.24","order":"06.05.035.4115"},["b","24"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"Keep"],"all the commandments and covenants by which ye are bound; and I will cause the heavens to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_24b"},"shake"],"for your",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_24c"},"good"],", and",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_24d"},"Satan"],"shall tremble and",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_24e"},"Zion"],"shall",["sup","f"],["a",{"href":"fn_24f"},"rejoice"],"upon the hills and",["sup","g"],["a",{"href":"fn_24g"},"flourish"],";"],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.25","order":"06.05.035.4116"},["b","25"],"And",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"Israel"],"shall be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_25b"},"saved"],"in mine own due time; and by the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_25c"},"keys"],"which I have given shall they be led, and no more be confounded at all."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.26","order":"06.05.035.4117"},["b","26"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"Lift"],"up your hearts and be glad, your",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_26b"},"redemption"],"draweth nigh."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.27","order":"06.05.035.4118"},["b","27"],"Fear not, little",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_27a"},"flock"],", the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_27b"},"kingdom"],"is yours until I come. Behold, I",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_27c"},"come"],"quickly. Even so. Amen."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.1a","order":"06.05.035.4119"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-lord"},"TG Jesus Christ, Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.1b","order":"06.05.035.4121"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/1.8"},"Rev. 1:8"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/19.1"},"D&C 19:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.1c","order":"06.05.035.4123"},["b","1c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/10.19"},"1 Ne. 10:19"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/3.2"},"D&C 3:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"1d","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.1d","order":"06.05.035.4125"},["b","1d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-eternal-nature-of"},"TG God, Eternal Nature of"],"."],["div",{"id":"1e","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.1e","order":"06.05.035.4127"},["b","1e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/13.8"},"Heb. 13:8"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/20.12"},"D&C 20:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.1.1-4"},"38:1 (1–4)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.1.1-3"},"39:1 (1–3)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/76.4"},"76:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.2a","order":"06.05.035.4129"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-crucifixion-of"},"TG Jesus Christ, Crucifixion of"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.2b","order":"06.05.035.4131"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/20.25"},"D&C 20:25"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.4"},"38:4"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/45.5.5,8"},"45:5 (5, 8)"],"."],["div",{"id":"2c","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.2c","order":"06.05.035.4133"},["b","2c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sons-and-daughters-of-god"},"TG Sons and Daughters of God"],"."],["div",{"id":"2d","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.2d","order":"06.05.035.4135"},["b","2d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/17.21"},"John 17:21"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/6.68"},"Moses 6:68"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/unity"},"TG Unity"],"."],["div",{"id":"2e","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.2e","order":"06.05.035.4137"},["b","2e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-exemplar"},"TG Jesus Christ, Exemplar"],"."],["div",{"id":"2f","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.2f","order":"06.05.035.4139"},["b","2f"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/godhead"},"TG Godhead"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.3a","order":"06.05.035.4141"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/2.24.23-24"},"Ex. 2:24 (23–24)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/9.18.17-18"},"Mosiah 9:18 (17–18)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/abr/1.15.15-16"},"Abr. 1:15 (15–16)"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.4a","order":"06.05.035.4143"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/mal/3.1"},"Mal. 3:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/11.10"},"Matt. 11:10"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/5.33"},"John 5:33"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/11.27"},"1 Ne. 11:27"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures